<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address - Veloura</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px; /* Adjust as needed for your logo */
            height: auto;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #007bff; /* Veloura primary color */
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #007bff; /* Veloura primary color */
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <% /* Uncomment and replace with your logo if you have one */ %>
            <!-- <img src="URL_TO_YOUR_VELOURA_LOGO" alt="Veloura Logo"> -->
            <h1>Welcome to Veloura!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for signing up for Veloura, your ultimate multi-vendor e-commerce destination!</p>
            <p>To complete your registration and unlock all the amazing features of Veloura, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="http://localhost:3000/auth/verify-email?token=<%= otp %>" class="button">Verify My Email</a>
            </div>
            <p>This link is valid for a limited time (5 minutes). If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following link into your web browser:</p>
            <p><a href="http://localhost:3000/auth/verify-email?token=<%= otp %>">http://localhost:3000/auth/verify-email?token=<%= otp %></a></p>
            <p>If you did not create an account with Veloura, please disregard this email.</p>
            <p>Happy Shopping and Selling on Veloura!</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Veloura Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Veloura. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><a href="YOUR_WEBSITE_PRIVACY_POLICY_URL">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="YOUR_WEBSITE_TERMS_OF_SERVICE_URL">Terms of Service</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
